description: Feeling a little down?  Haven't laughed all day?  Well, Comedy Dog comes to the rescue.  Armed with a large portfolio or hilarious jokes (mostly about dogs), just start up Comedy Dog and get ready to laugh.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Comedy Dog to tell me a joke.
Alexa, ask Comedy Dog to make me laugh.
name: Comedy Dog
shortDescription: Comedy Dog is here to entertain you with a series of excellent jokes.
